:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇唔出佢幾有腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高學歷=聰明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 咁都唔聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下考10a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書唔叻唔一定蠢<br />\n但讀書叻蠢極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到學歷高嘅人就最鍾意話佢冇street smart<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d524e20351ef716ca0e0aea28cdd1da3d41ab35f","tid":286682,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"其實覺得佢同何浩文好襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想佢地一齊"},{"pid":"183527667e56d8a1421da0ebbbd36e8141ab3599","tid":286682,"uid":35701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2485ef57ae0a582774590543d401814d4991d3f1","tid":286682,"uid":32280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但起碼我眼見好多師奶見佢10A 就當佢神咁拜<br />\n佢鬧七警 鬧政府啲師奶因為佢學歷<br />\n覺得好有道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都算係件好事？</blockquote><br />\n得罪哂撐黑警果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b79c824f4b9848988730e98e950031f1cae81e","tid":286682,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"咁都無樣無野好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c52fd1fbe2aecd0a0feb6690f190afaabc2ec4f","tid":286682,"uid":85238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多界港姐冠軍最醜就係佢</blockquote><br />\n張嘉兒都啱啊？你都幾重口味啦"},{"pid":"a5eb55e1ffd49e04ca04bae0b1840bdc3eea6ab0","tid":286682,"uid":54079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇唔出佢幾有腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高學歷=聰明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係掛 咁都唔聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下考10a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書唔叻唔一定蠢<br />\n但讀書叻蠢極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢根本冇論據就拋啲垃圾觀點出嚟<br />\n點解噉嘅字都可以打得落手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只可以講佢聰明嘅地方係在於識包裝自己嘅形象<br />\n佢知道10A同法律系畢業係自己嘅優勢佢就識去善用<br />\n馮盈盈都叫HKU 畢業 佢同麥明詩應該都係黃絲<br />\n但點解馮盈盈形象咁差？佢可以討得班師奶歡心？<br />\n馮盈盈講完粗口話自己係年少無知 結果咪俾人再鬧得勁啲<br />\n麥明詩就回應話有好多說話比粗口更加難聽<br />\n又話係人都有講過粗口<br />\n<br />\n你講麥明詩口才同演戲就一定唔係勁架啦<br />\n樣都唔係出眾 更加唔岩做娛樂圈添<br />\n但我始終覺得有個咁嘅人係而家嘅娛樂圈唔係一件壞事<br />\n始終唔同嘅政治事件佢都敢發言<br />\n（就算話佢想搏出位 但真係佢包裝得唔差）<br />\n令到當佢神咁拜個班師奶有返少少腦<br />\n有冇論據就見人見智啦 對班師奶嚟講佢嘅說話真係好有論據架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494d76f7cc2b6ee0fcfcb2e68fdf3623d34e30ea","tid":286682,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁多界港姐冠軍最醜就係佢</blockquote><br />\n咁你又離譜D</blockquote><br />\n邵珮詩先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140827/photo/bkntw-20140827155129488-0827_04111_001_02b.jpg?172936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140827%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20140827155129488-0827_04111_001_02b.jpg%3F172936&h=ce805eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邵珮詩唔錯喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢做愛回家同依家8點個出戲都好撚on9 一把年紀扮得意同天真小妹妹 把聲又扮可愛 聽佢講野就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小pussy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢喉嚨發炎應該係最perfect"},{"pid":"92c68200ce50abb1220d70d3f95ff33b91d5bcf7","tid":286682,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d9299f38a6dda454d9813071f029364d7e3424b","tid":286682,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"我 覺得好正"},{"pid":"3cc55c081e6018c9f928bdf0724a9a8ff5e652bd","tid":286682,"uid":92072,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得而家啲港姐冇乜本土味 好多都係外國返黎 唔似港人<br />\n反而麥明詩有港女嘅感覺 呢種女當選到港姐其實幾難得 所以我覺得佢幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447e11797ea9dc64f16afb9c128ea15f9d6246e4","tid":286682,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>second low入唔到pcll<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劍橋 2nd up入唔到pcll ?<br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cb5db30b234ea8d0eaaeaa47122a9b56834ba6","tid":286682,"uid":28888,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇唔出佢幾有腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高學歷=聰明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://eweekly.hk/article/_title/擘大口食蛋撻失儀_麥明詩最好用鹽水袋隊落血管_61o