e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼佢敢言 淨係呢樣已經欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n同埋關心社會"},{"pid":"1b67ad2c0953f4f7d98c79915a884a61c188ed84","tid":286682,"uid":87339,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果屌到麥明詩呢d級數就真係無憾<br />\n大大力推車打屎忽<br />\n諗起佢10A讀牛津都要俾我屌到啊啊聲<br />\n果種征服感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢劍橋啊<br />\n<br />\n牛津個個係林作<br />\n<br />\n推車都推錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeae228c0481822a587c75470d366408973e755d","tid":286682,"uid":19275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"唔識演戲=無實力<br />\n幾時開始做港姐要識做戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a86795f94408e9b4d675a887a09ab71eacb0861","tid":286682,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:49:53.000Z","msg":"就係你呢啲人搞到港姐變左港雞"},{"pid":"59babdfd571112c41bbeb417b0e2f4bd790d9b21","tid":286682,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"林作你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8800e7fea970b7d94d92323217e6a7e44b4e2c2","tid":286682,"uid":8167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識演戲=無實力<br />\n幾時開始做港姐要識做戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />